{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "🎛️ RHINOMETRIC Control Center",
    "tags": ["rhinometric", "control", "admin"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "schemaVersion": 38,
    "version": 0,
    "refresh": "5s",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "type": "text",
        "title": "🚀 Welcome to RHINOMETRIC v2.4.0",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 0,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 3
        },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "# 🎛️ RHINOMETRIC Control Center\n\n**Platform Observability & Management Console**\n\n- 🔗 **API Connector**: Create and manage data source connections\n- 📊 **Dashboard Builder**: Design custom monitoring dashboards\n- 📈 **System Metrics**: Real-time platform health monitoring\n\n**Quick Links**: [Grafana](/) | [Prometheus](http://localhost:9090) | [Tempo](http://localhost:3200) | [Loki](http://localhost:3100)\n\n---"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "type": "row",
        "title": "🔗 API Connector",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 3,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 1
        },
        "collapsed": false
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "type": "text",
        "title": "About API Connector",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 6,
          "h": 8
        },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "## 🔗 API Connector\n\n**Create data source connections**\n\nSupported types:\n- PostgreSQL\n- MySQL\n- InfluxDB\n- MongoDB\n- Elasticsearch\n- Prometheus\n- Loki\n- Tempo\n\n**Features**:\n- ✅ Connection testing\n- ✅ Auto-provisioning\n- ✅ Grafana integration\n- ✅ Connection history"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "type": "text",
        "title": "⚠️ Iframe Notice",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 6,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 18,
          "h": 2
        },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "⚠️ **Security Notice**: Iframe content requires proper CSP headers. If you see \"Refused to display in frame\", this is expected browser behavior.\n\n**Alternative Access**: Open directly at [http://localhost:8000](http://localhost:8000)"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "type": "text",
        "title": "API Connector Interface",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 6,
          "y": 6,
          "w": 18,
          "h": 18
        },
        "options": {
          "mode": "html",
          "content": "<iframe src=\"http://localhost:8000\" width=\"100%\" height=\"800\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"></iframe>"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "API Connector Status",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 12,
          "w": 3,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up{job=\"api-connector\"}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {
                "type": "value",
                "options": {
                  "0": {
                    "text": "DOWN",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  "1": {
                    "text": "UP",
                    "color": "green"
                  }
                }
              }
            ],
            "color": {
              "mode": "thresholds"
            },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "value": 0,
                  "color": "red"
                },
                {
                  "value": 1,
                  "color": "green"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Response Time",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 3,
          "y": 12,
          "w": 3,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(http_request_duration_seconds_sum{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m]) / rate(http_request_duration_seconds_count{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "s",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 1,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "value": 0,
                  "color": "green"
                },
                {
                  "value": 0.5,
                  "color": "yellow"
                },
                {
                  "value": 0.8,
                  "color": "red"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 8,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Total Requests",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 16,
          "w": 3,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m]))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "reqps",
            "color": {
              "mode": "palette-classic"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 9,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Error Rate",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 3,
          "y": 16,
          "w": 3,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"api-connector\",status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])) * 100",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "color": {
              "mode": "thresholds"
            },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "value": 0,
                  "color": "green"
                },
                {
                  "value": 1,
                  "color": "yellow"
                },
                {
                  "value": 5,
                  "color": "red"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 10,
        "type": "row",
        "title": "📊 Dashboard Builder",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 24,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 1
