        "title": "About Dashboard Builder",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 25,
          "w": 6,
          "h": 8
        },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "## 📊 Dashboard Builder\n\n**Visual dashboard designer**\n\nFeatures:\n- 📋 Pre-built templates\n- 🎨 Drag & drop editor\n- 📊 Panel library\n- 🔗 Datasource integration\n- 💾 Save to PostgreSQL\n- 🚀 Deploy to Grafana\n\n**Templates**:\n- System Metrics\n- API Monitoring\n- Database Performance\n- Custom Design"
        }
      },
